title: Ultimate Incredible Hulk Comics Collection (.cbz files)
description:
This collection contains nearly 600 Hulk comics going back to issue #1. It includes all of the Tales to Astonish issues, the Hulk annuals, and more, all as individual .cbz files. Pick and choose the issues you want, or download the entire collection.

I was a Hulk fanatic when I was a kid (still kinda am), and it gives me great pleasure to bring you this amazing collection. 'Nuff said.

Seed, or HULK SMASH!

Cheers!
